title: Priorities
description:
Tony Kornheiser and Pablo Torre discuss the Bucs’ coaching change, Brian Cashman blaming the Astros for the Yankees not making the 2017 World Series and country music artist Eric Church canceling his concert to watch UNC vs. Duke.
